{"tid":1771707,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【課金幫拖】有網上媒體眾籌！幫拖啦！","createTime":"2019-12-06T05:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T07:35:18.000Z","uid":1851,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22abd138be3df421add299c7e4c03d9b90c9f5cb","tid":1771707,"uid":1851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">話說我個friend同佢老細搞左個媒體，叫《誌》（係facebook、ig（hk_feature) 同youtube都有）。（網站都有但好初步，因為真係唔夠人手搞....)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地專拍紀錄片，同埋做新聞專題。成場運動經常會去現場採訪。但係呢壇野出左黎半年，本身係想做香港不同領域的新聞專題，但咁啱有呢場運動，所以大部分時間都係去抗爭現場拍。全部都係佢老細畀錢自己搞（其實真係搵唔到錢....)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實個眾籌都開始左成個月，本身佢地想籌600萬台幣，但而家連第一階段100萬台幣都唔到，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果第一階段唔夠，基本上佢地一毫子都無，眾籌平台會全數退款。</span></span></strong> 其實好多page都share過佢地啲相（keochow同上帝都有），之前拍外國人唱榮光都係佢地拍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點黎啦，搞咁多野，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">間公司其實得三個人</span></strong>（連埋老細），<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">蘋果果籽都有訪問過佢地</span></span></strong>，想知多啲就睇下啦<br />\nLINK：<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191205/60342221?fbclid=IwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60342221%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScPdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=2d01c37d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60342221%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&h=3bfaf848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191205/60342221?fbclid=IwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4</a><a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191205/60342221?fbclid=IwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60342221%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScPdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=54d9d6a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F60342221%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4&h=202ceeff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191205/60342221?fbclid=IwAR3RyRM3MjJOnhw5dAx1uxyL2MZsbClJ-DYcBnm1Y3pAAxKlLZy5haPeib4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/06/123828_bda35c624cd3c862db801eda8aa94bda.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F123828_bda35c624cd3c862db801eda8aa94bda.jpeg&h=3e4f882b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地眾籌平台用台灣平台，叫flying V，因為佢地想做兩地專題，順便做宣傳，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係之前林榮基係台灣開返銅鑼灣書店眾籌用嗰個</span></span></strong>。但有個唔方便位，就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">顯示金額係台幣</span></span></strong>。有個100台幣option，其實只係25港幣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾籌LINK：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.flyingv.cc/projects/24455?fbclid=IwAR0zwypdflKiY1ybQDnIOZvPwH4h4YcTeMhLQoUvktg6eAMnPd-uQL5JtAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyingv.cc%2Fprojects%2F24455%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0zwypdflKiY1ybQDnIOZvPwH4h4YcTeMhLQoUvktg6eAMnPd-uQL5JtAg%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScPdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=fabd9f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.flyingv.cc/projects/24455?fbclid=IwAR0zwypdflKiY1ybQDnIOZvPwH4h4YcTeMhLQoUvktg6eAMnPd-uQL5JtAg</a><a href=\"https://www.flyingv.cc/projects/24455?fbclid=IwAR0zwypdflKiY1ybQDnIOZvPwH4h4YcTeMhLQoUvktg6eAMnPd-uQL5JtAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyingv.cc%2Fprojects%2F24455%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0zwypdflKiY1ybQDnIOZvPwH4h4YcTeMhLQoUvktg6eAMnPd-uQL5JtAg&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScPdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=b780ffb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.flyingv.cc/projects/24455?fbclid=IwAR0zwypdflKiY1ybQDnIOZvPwH4h4YcTeMhLQoUvktg6eAMnPd-uQL5JtAg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/06/130543_5af1a7800430e71051822754a6f2d2ac.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F130543_5af1a7800430e71051822754a6f2d2ac.jpeg&h=1b57ff3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpofARW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpofARW.jpg&h=8f6e321d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家應該得250人捐左，佢地希望至少有1000人，做到真正集資。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔課都好，關注下佢地，我個frd話超多五毛留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家有錢的就去課下金，支持下小媒體，</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學立場匡哥話齋，「請大家支持所有香港公民社會上，你認為值得支持的媒體與組織。」你懲罰黃店都唔會淨係懲罰一間啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫拖啊手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528ed0708c1e52c03a86aa41208da2e484a6a4e4","tid":1771707,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"4e57b6e99fc276f7198122c4c4303b